cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses unsupervised deep learning for computer vision tasks, specifically image classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel approach to unsupervised learning, which could fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The method involves discovering neighbourhoods of samples, which could also relate to the categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
